It has become apparent to me that it is still not the right time. This journal may become "friends only" sooner than later. I dont need to search for anything, I can just block anyone who is not my livejournal friend already.


ain't that a bitch?

livejournal it has been awhile.
but you know i turn to you only when I dont know where else to turn.
i feel as if i cant complain
but all i have are complaints
what do i want?
if i knew that, making logical decisions would be easier
but what about when you dont know what you want
what about when you think you know what you want but you were mistaken
is what you think you want what you really need? or is it what you want?
the min dplays tricks against itsself and once you come to that realization 
it leaves you lost and confused
because you dont know who to trust, you cant even trust yourself anymore
is it in your power to obtain what you want? (or what you think you want)
or do you constantly struggle trying to make the right decisions based on the lies that you tell yourself?
it is a perpetual state of confusion and though it is contained it festers
hope starts to die
are your dreams and aspirations actually your dreams and aspirations? or did you just tell yourself that enough for long enough that it becomes your pseudoreality?
WHATS THE FUCKING ANSWER!?
what do you do
go with the flow? who knows where that will take you

all i know is something isnt right
and for the first time, i dont know what it is
so you search
you try new things
even some things you shouldnt have
but you still feel empty
you wake up excited for something

but that something never comes
you end the day just as sad as it began

i dont want to type anymore
i dont even know who still reads this

im just sick of fighting with myself

Here we go down that same old road again
Sympathy unfolds the shell that holds all the beauty within

We must push on, we must push on
Though we bleed
We must push on, we must push on

Theyre bloodshot now but theyll be black by dawn

You need people like me so you can point your fuckin' fingers and say, "That's the bad guy." So... what that make you? Good? You're not good. You just know how to hide, how to lie. Me, I don't have that problem. Me, I always tell the truth. Even when I lie. So say good night to the bad guy! Come on. The last time you gonna see a bad guy like this again, let me tell you. Come on. Make way for the bad guy. There's a bad guy comin' through! Better get outta his way!

is this week over yet?


is this year over yet?

I can feel the muscles in my neck and shoulders tightening up as the weeks go by.

Anyone want to go get a massage with me?

That or we need to throw a massage party.

or orgy.

I've been quick to just blow off a lot of things that would bother me, espescialy when it comes to people. But recently shitty people have started to get to me, at work, while Im driving, in my everyday life..... So all I have to say is this. Fuck Shitty People "god will bless you if you make us a good deal on this saxophone....."
Its good to get high again, and not just stoned.

Can the experiences one goes through break down certain emotional barriers that had been put into place?

The answer is yes. 

I've felt some feelings recently that I havent felt in a very long time, some good, some bad.
Im not quite sure what to make of them all, and I dont know what has triggered it all. I dont know if this journal and reading back through old entries has brought back some of my past issues that I thought had been dealt with. 

All I know is I feel very fragile and I've never had this much of an urge to get completely wasted. 

Everything happens for a reason, and theres a party tonight.

On a side note, I found out today that I need new tires.

Goddamnit.

I feel as though I can think more clearly now
The obstacles and obstructions on the path to my goals are more evident to me now

Its unsettling

I have been putting off everything that I haven't been ready to deal with, and that seems to be a common theme in my life

I miss my fraternity. 
I just have an issue being halfway involved. I want to do everything or nothing at all.

I want to make music again, I want to feel creative and I want to feel as if I haven't lost touch with my passion.

But Im only one man. 

One man pulled in thousands of directions.

I've got a lot of growing up to do.

I feel taken advantage of.


But I feel taken advantage of by me.

The difference between Eye Opening and Life Altering lies solely in Initiative. I had to have a thought present to spark a post, but I dont have too much to say, not right now at least. I think I just have an aversion to LiveJournal. I never used it as an informative tool I never really posted when I was happy It was release It was comfort It was a crutch. But I realized you dont always have to be in a bad emotional state to document your feelings I was reading back and I wish I had posted about more of the happy times and the good feelings I had Because all I have to show for those times are my memories. and memories fade over time......

oh shit.

I forgot I had one of these.

Life is good.

I miss everyone here.

If you want to catch up, leave me a comment and we will.

The only thing that could make me an happier right now would be true love.

But who even knows if thats real.......

Was it worth 80 bucks? Maybe Was it worth the hassle of finding a florist to deliver on such short notice? Maybe Was it worth hearing the sound of her voice when she called me and was estatic? DEFINATELY.

Why do I always put myself in less than desirable situations? Why do I always get myself into situations that cause nothing but unnecessary stress? Is there something wrong with me? Or is there something wrong with everyone else...... I just don't understand what is going on I've always been able to read people But I can't read her Today just hasn't been the best day I feel it in me So overwhelmed Oh this pressured center rising My life over turned Unfair the despair All these scars keep ripping open In this hole That is me Left with a heart exhausted Whats my release? What sets me free? Do you pull me up just to push me down again? Peel me from the skin Tear me from the bone Does it make you happy now?

I guess im too lazy to make real entries anymore. I guess I will keep posting lyrics that sum up my feelings. I found that fucking song again. This is fucking pitiful. Im sinking lower and lower everyday And my bright days grow duller as each day passes. Its a shame you gotta put on makeup today I think you look so fine You look best when you rise Where did you go You were here yesterday Why did you leave? Why did you leave? And now I'm stuck here thinking about your face Why am I so weak? Why am I so weak? When you were here we did nothing but fight But now that you're gone my life has no light I really want to work this out But 20 excuses come out of your mouth I once felt strong It wouldn't last for long I wrap my hands around my neck Kill myself again Cut my arms with the biggest knife that I can stand Why waste time Lifting my head Keep it down And save face instead I hate myself, more than I ever let on. I lived too fast and I loved too much and I'll die too young, but I chose this cup that I drank from. Knew what I was getting into. But I couldn't let out what I had to keep in. I'm ashamed of myself and unspeakable sins, that I've committed and I've made mistakes, but I'll find my way. There's no explanation for, the things I've failed at before. They can't hold my hand. It just hurts to be a man, Through the tortures of the damned If I only had an axe, I'd sever the ties I've made with the world. Maybe I can be a stranger, in a strange place. If I start now, maybe I can be saved. If I only had a mask, I'd cover these bleeding eyes. They're bloodshot now but they'll be black by dawn. If I wake up now, I can be pure again.

Last night was pretty amazing, I will admit.
Not only did I learn so much about myself, but the connections I made with other people made me feel very warm in this cold and lonely world.

I need to start writing again.
No more excuses.
